<h1>Our features</h1>
<p class="intro">
    Welcome to <strong>AnswerNest</strong>. This platform is built for people to ask questions,
    share knowledge, and help others. To keep the community helpful and respectful,
    all users must follow these guidelines.
</p>

<hr>

<p>Smart Search — Search questions by keyword, tag, or category before posting
Tags & Categories — Label questions with relevant topics for easy discovery
Upvote / Downvote — Let the community rank the most helpful answers
Accepted Answer — Question authors can mark one answer as the best solution
Rich Text Editor — Format answers with bold, code blocks, lists, and links</p>

<h2>User & Profile Features</h2>

<ul>
    <li>Reputation System — Earn points for asking good questions and giving helpful answers</li>
<li>Badges & Achievements — Reward active contributors (e.g. "First Answer", "Top Helper")</li>
<li>User Profiles — Show a user's questions, answers, and reputation score</li>
<li>Follow Users — Get notified when someone you follow posts or answers</li>
</ul>

<h2>Discovery & Engagement</h2>

<ul>
    <li>Trending Questions — Show hot or popular questions on the homepage</li>
    <li>Related Questions — Suggest similar questions while someone is typing</li>
    <li>Bookmarks / Save — Let users save questions to revisit later</li>
    <li>Comment Threads — Allow short comments under answers for clarification</li>
</ul>

<h2>Notifications & Communication</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Real-time Notifications — Alert users when their question gets an answer or comment</li>
    <li>Email Digest — Weekly summary of top questions in topics you follow</li>
    <li>Mention System — Tag other users with @username in answers</li>
</ul>

<h2>Moderation & Trust</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Report System — Flag inappropriate content for moderator review</li>
    <li>Edit History — Track changes made to questions and answers</li>
    <li>Verified Answers — Moderators can verify technically accurate answers</li>
</ul>

<h2>Admin / Moderator Tools</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Dashboard — View reported posts, user activity, and site stats</li>
    <li>Ban / Suspend Users — Handle accounts that violate guidelines</li>
    <li>Pinned Announcements — Post important updates site-wide</li>
</ul>
</div>
<%- include("partials/footer") %>
</body>
</html>
